                        <h2>Temporary Leasing</h2>

<p><strong>Temporary Leasing &amp; Advertising Opportunities at Cloverdale Mall</strong></p>

<p>Our cart/kiosk/in-line program is designed for seasonal, established and/or new retailers alike. The program is flexible and affordable enough for even first-time retailers to test the market for their new or one-of-a-kind product(s). Please note that ALL RETAILERS MUST HAVE A BUSINESS LICENSE AND PROVIDE INSURANCE.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>&quot;RMUs&quot; (Carts)</strong></p>

<p>Our cart program is professionally managed by Cart Wheels International Inc., whose services beyond location include product development, display merchandising and marketing. For more information regarding Cart Wheels International Inc. and their many services; visit www.cartwheelsinternational.com or contact Susan Dennis directly at 905-855-1616 or 1-800-236-1591 or <a href="mailto:cartwheels@on.aibn.com">cartwheels@on.aibn.com</a></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>&quot;KIOSKs&quot; (Common Area Displays)</strong></p>

<p>Bring your specialized display to Cloverdale Mall, our common area program offers your product exposure at affordable rates. Displays must be professional in nature, and sizing can vary dependent upon location within the centre.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>&quot;IN-LINE&quot; (Store)</strong></p>

<p>Looking to give a store front location a try? Big or small, Cloverdale could be the new location of that next big thing, YOU! Sizes, availability and duration vary.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>ADVERTISING: LARGE FORMAT ADVERTISING</strong></p>

<p>Door decals, floor decals, table-top &quot;talkers&quot;, exterior displays, digital sign boards, static posters &ndash; options galore. Our advertising program is professionally managed by Pattison OneStop, an industry leader in large format advertising.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>Short-term Store Unit Application</strong></p>

<p>For those interested in applying for a Short-term Store Unit, please send the required information outlines below in an email to Lisa Peatt, General Manager <a href="mailto:lpeatt@bentallkennedy.com">lpeatt@bentallkennedy.com</a></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<ul>
	<li>Doing Business As</li>
	<li>Describe your product and merchandising concept</li>
	<li>Price Point(s)</li>
	<li>Projected Sales per Week</li>
	<li>Target Market</li>
	<li>Are you operating this business elsewhere now?</li>
	<li>Type of space? Example: Kiosk/In Line</li>
	<li>Size of Space preferred</li>
	<li>Have you previously set-up in a mall environment?
	<ul style="list-style-type:circle">
		<li>If yes, indicate where:</li>
	</ul>
	</li>
	<li>Your Name, Phone Number and Email Address</li>
	<li>A detailed sketch and or photos of previous set-ups must accompany this application</li>
</ul>

